I would like to have ability to see the last time a comment has been edited.

Currently an edited comment may be seen as having the creation timestamp and marking that it is edited, e.g.:
{code}05/Mar/13 01:19 PM - edited{code}

What I would like to have is something like
{code}05/Mar/13 01:19 PM - edited at 14/Mar/13 4:56 AM{code}
To have both creation and last edit timestamps.

I envision it as adding one extra timestamp field for the comments data-table.

P.S.
This should not pose a security risk as is tracking the history of commments (this is NOT JRA-12400)

